==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Boasting
<hw>Boast"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act of glorying or vaunting;
vainglorious speaking; ostentatious display.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>When <qex>boasting</qex> ends, then dignity begins.</q>
<rj><qau>Young.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Boastingly</ent>⟦br⟧
